_sText:
This is my new map, it's called surf_treespam. My goal was to make a difficult map while keeping the annoying factor down, which I think I achieved.

Try to enjoy it, but be warned, it is quite hard.

Difficulty (determined by beta tester feedback): Tier 6/6

Surf timer zoning information is included in the zip file.
